      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃんには待ってもらうようにお願いしたけど）\n（私……どうしたらいいんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I asked Kotono-chan to wait for me‚ but…)\n(What… what should I do?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1999999046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "（私がついて行っちゃったら）\n（月ストは本当にバラバラになっちゃう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(If I go with her‚)\n(Moon Tempest will really fall apart.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、私がアイドルになった理由は）\n（琴乃ちゃんを応援して、支えるためで……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But the reason I became an idol…)\n(was to support and be there for Kotono-chan…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3999999046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん……大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan… Are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8246248882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ごめん\nちょっと考え事してて、あはは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Sorry.\nI was just lost in thought‚ ahaha…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、私達の間で隠し事など不要ですわよ？\nほら、早く話してごらんなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ there’s no need for secrets between us‚ right?\nCome on‚ tell us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7505656879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "す～ず～にゃ～ん。ほいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suuuzuuu-nyaaan. Heyyy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5172322274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "もがが～！？　何するんですの～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha—!? What are you doing~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6172322274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "今はレッスン中ですし、深くは聞きませんが……\n私達ならいつでも話を聞きますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in the middle of a lesson‚ so I won’t ask too much…\nbut we’re always here to listen if you need to talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6505656879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5838988941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 58.1400436879
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "浅い悩みでも深い悩みでも、どんときなさい！\n私が鮮やかに解決してみせますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether it’s a small worry or a big worry‚ bring it on!\nI’ll solve it for you brilliantly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9258222491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……ありがと、元気出たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… Thanks‚ I feel better now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3067103546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、元気が一番！\nそれじゃ、そろそろ再開しよっか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah yeah‚ it’s best to be cheerful!\nSo‚ shall we resume soon?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6680707455,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.3332061999927,
          "startTime": 74.8014039517
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、もう十分休んだと思う。始めようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think we’ve rested enough. Let’s get started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8014039517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな、私のこと心配してくれてる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Everyone’s worried about me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.634737285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、私のことだけじゃない）\n（今の琴乃ちゃんのことも気付いて、心配してる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But it’s not just about me.)\n(They’ve noticed Kotono-chan’s current state‚ and they’re worried about her too.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "（お互いの些細な変化も気付けるくらい……）\n（私達はずっと一緒にやってきたんだよね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We’ve been together so long that we can even notice each other’s subtle changes…)\n(We really have come a long way‚ haven’t we?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――渚、オフの日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Nagisa‚ day off",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5978236516,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6585287000003,
          "startTime": 98.9644821803
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.7978236516
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.7978236516
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 98.9644821803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。一人で来るのっていつぶりだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew. I wonder how long it’s been since I came here alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6311508815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.6906518937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "電車で隣に琴乃ちゃんがいないのが\nなんだか変な感じだったなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels weird not having Kotono-chan next to me\non the subway…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.9223521551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "……とりあえず、ブラついてみよっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I guess I’ll just wander around for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9223521551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.9136445206
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.9136445206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……ここは変わらないなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… This place hasn’t changed at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9636445206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.6480765231
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.1774797441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだ未熟ですが、私達はともに切磋琢磨し\n刺激し合いながら成長していきたいと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re still immature‚ but we want to grow by working hard together\nand stimulating each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.7774797441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "この場所で、月ストとサニピが生まれたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace were born in this place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8108068467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0867702326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだか、すっごく前のことに思えちゃうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It feels like it happened such a long time ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0867702326,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5174.875148199988,
          "startTime": 141.2616453808
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.0116453808
    },
